  "prompt": "Create an image depicting the common symbol of blockchain technology, which is a series of interconnected blocks or cells linked by lines. This design should visually illustrate the chain-like, sequential nature of data records in blockchain, where each block of information is connected to the previous one, forming a continuous chain of data. The image should be simple, with a focus on the interconnected blocks to clearly convey the concept of blockchain's linked data structure.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
